### Day 2 Testing - DTOs, Validation, and Swagger
### Use REST Client extension in VS Code or copy to Postman

### Test 1: Valid Payload (Should return 201)
POST http://localhost:3000/sample
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "age": 25
}

###

### Test 2: Invalid Email (Should return 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/sample
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "invalid-email",
  "age": 25
}

###

### Test 3: Missing Required Fields (Should return 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/sample
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "age": 25
}

###

### Test 4: Unknown Fields - forbidNonWhitelisted (Should return 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/sample
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "age": 25,
  "unknownField": "should be rejected",
  "anotherUnknown": "also rejected"
}

###

### Test 5: Invalid Age Range (Should return 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/sample
